  {
    "id": "2077115165871677689",
    "text": "Iran’s Revolutionary Guards (IRGC) says that as long as US “evil actions” continue in the region, “not a single drop of oil and gas” will be exported from the region, Iranian state media reports.\n\nIRGC also says US “aggressions” will have no result other than to delay the reopening of the Strait of Hormuz, adding that their attacks on what it described as US facilities in Kuwait and Bahrain came in response to US attacks on Iran.\nhttps://t.co/ddciAby3M2",
